<h4><a href="http://mo.techweb.com.cn/digi/2020-08-26/2802076.shtml">怒喵科技推出一系列亚文化潮流无线桌面产品</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361215" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2_6b113b4793f346a789ad00080b752e76_img_jpg.jpeg" alt="" width="1489" height="785" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2_6b113b4793f346a789ad00080b752e76_img_jpg.jpeg 1489w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2_6b113b4793f346a789ad00080b752e76_img_jpg-360x190.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2_6b113b4793f346a789ad00080b752e76_img_jpg-768x405.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/v2_6b113b4793f346a789ad00080b752e76_img_jpg-1024x540.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1489px) 100vw, 1489px" /></p>
<p>TechWeb 消息，由李楠创办的怒喵科技宣布创立无线桌面品牌 NOWIRE，愿景为三年之内去掉身上和桌面上所有的线，首个系列灵感来自 Tesla Cybertruck，包括 CYBERMAT 充电毯、CYBERBOARD 机械键盘、CYBERCOIN 鼠标配件，预告了 CYBERBLADE TWS 真无线蓝牙降噪耳机。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361217" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6373405109638959418276113-1.jpg" alt="" width="638" height="338" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6373405109638959418276113-1.jpg 638w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/6373405109638959418276113-1-360x191.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px" /></p>
<p>CYBERMAT 可同时支持 6 个设备无线充电；CYBERBOARD 机械键盘具有自定义 LED 灯阵，同时支持蓝牙无线传输、并支持无线充电；CYBERCOIN 改装套件可以让鼠标获得通用无线充电能力。最后怒喵预告了 CYBERBLADE 耳机，表示它将「强调亚文化表达」，机身呈三角形，预计于 12 月发布。</p>
